CSS custom properties or CSS defined variables 



1. we can specify the variable in the ":root" pseudo classs as below:

	syntax :
			
				:root {
				
					--color-primary-light: red;
					--color-primary:dark: yellow;
					--u-margin-bottom: 8rem;
					--shadow-color: 0rem 2rem 3rem rgba(balck,0.4);
				
				}
				
				
				body {
				
					background-image: linear-radient(to right bottom,var(--color-primary-light),var(--color-primary:dark));
					margin-bootm: var(--u-margin-bottom);
					box-shadow: var(--shadow-color);
				
				}